General.Name: Krungdhep Sophon Public Company Limited
General.Description: Krungdhep Sophon Public Company Limited engages in the development and leasing of real estate properties in Thailand. The company also operates warehouse and wharf business that offers space renting and port of loading/unloading goods to retail customers. In addition, it provides document storage and management services; and computer backup media services. The company was formerly known as Krungdhep Warehouse Company Limited and changed its name to Krungdhep Sophon Public Company Limited in December 1995. Krungdhep Sophon Public Company Limited was founded in 1961 and is headquartered in Bangkok, Thailand.
